listitem.para:
SQL no matter ascending or descending - query returns result
            nodes in random order: {code}SELECT * FROM nt:unstructured WHERE
            jcr:path LIKE 'testRoot/%' ORDER BY jcr:path{code}

XPath - jcr:path order construction is ignored (so result is
            not sorted according path); {code}/testRoot/* @jcr:primaryType='nt:unstructured'
            order by jcr:path{code}

